&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;THE OPPORTUNITY&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;The way B2B revenue teams&amp;nbsp;operate&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;fundamentally reshaped by&amp;nbsp;AI&amp;nbsp;and most organizations&amp;nbsp;haven’t&amp;nbsp;caught up yet. The ones that move now&amp;nbsp;won’t&amp;nbsp;just be more efficient;&amp;nbsp;they’ll&amp;nbsp;see things their competitors&amp;nbsp;can’t&amp;nbsp;see, act on signals others miss, and compound that advantage quarter after quarter.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We’re&amp;nbsp;building a Revenue Operations function designed for this moment. Not a back-office reporting team, but an operational intelligence engine that sits at the heart of how we generate, convert, and grow revenue. This role is central to that ambition.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;As our AI-Enabled Revenue Operations Specialist, you will own three interconnected missions:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;•&quot; data-font=&quot;&quot; data-listid=&quot;7&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:540,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;•&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Revenue Insights &amp;amp; Reporting:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Build AI-enhanced analytics across the full funnel — pipeline health, conversion dynamics, QBR narratives, revenue forecasting — turning fragmented data into decisions that leadership and frontline teams act on weekly, not quarterly.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:80,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
