&lt;p&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://3339696.fs1.hubspotusercontent-na1.net/hubfs/3339696/greenhouse_hero.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;900&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;OUR VISION&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When people use our technology to &quot;bridge the gap&quot; between the physical and digital worlds, they don’t just capture reality - they create a new one. In this new reality, they are smarter, more productive, more streamlined, and more creative - because they have the digital foundation to build the world they want to live in.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That’s what NavVis offers in all our products and services: the tools to not just map the world as it is, but to pave the way to a better future. To forge something new. Physical or digital, there is only one reality. And it’s the reality NavVis empowers people to build better.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;THE OPPORTUNITY&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Does the&amp;nbsp;opportunity to work on the most&amp;nbsp;advanced Indoor&amp;nbsp;Mobile Mapping System excite you?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;As an Assembly Technician in our diverse and international Hardware Development and Operations team, you will get to work on assembling&amp;nbsp;cutting-edge&amp;nbsp;technology, while growing and developing yourself in the process. People that are part of this team have transformed the spatial technology industry by scaling up the production of our mobile scanning devices, NavVis&amp;nbsp;VLX&amp;nbsp;and MLX.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;If you are someone with a technical bent of mind, some&amp;nbsp;initial&amp;nbsp;hands-on experience in assembling, and are highly motivated to learn new things, this might be the right position for you!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
