&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;This role is ideal for someone who combines technical curiosity with creativity, adapting their approach to each client’s needs. If you have a business mindset, a genuine interest in the latest spatial and surveying technologies, and the drive to exceed targets,&amp;nbsp;we’d&amp;nbsp;love to hear from you!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
