&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;6956&quot; data-local-id=&quot;7c18a1c1a693&quot;&gt;This role operates on a late-shift schedule (&lt;strong&gt;1:00 PM – 9:00 PM CEST&lt;/strong&gt;) to support our globally distributed project teams across the US and Canada.&lt;/p&gt;
