&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;7279&quot; data-local-id=&quot;8760abb1993d&quot;&gt;After a structured onboarding, you&#39;ll work with diverse spatial data including 3D scans, point clouds, floor plans, panoramic images, and 3D models&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
