&lt;h3&gt;WIE WIR WISSEN, OB WIR PERFEKT ZUEINANDER PASSEN&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Deine Ansprechpartnerin für diese Stelle ist Lenka (sie/ihr). Es erwarten dich ein Auswahlgespräch und b

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://3339696.fs1.hubspotusercontent-na1.net/hubfs/3339696/greenhouse_hero.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;900&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;OUR VISION&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When people use our technology to &quot;bridge the gap&quot; between the physical and digital worlds, they don’t just capture reality - they create a new one. In this new reality, they are smarter, more productive, more streamlined, and more creative - because they have the digital foundation to build the world they want to live in.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That’s what NavVis offers in all our products and services: the tools to not just map the world as it is, but to pave the way to a better future. To forge something new. Physical or digital, there is only one reality. And it’s the reality NavVis empowers people to build better.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;THE OPPORTUNITY&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Does the opportunity to&amp;nbsp;contribute to the strategic vision and roadmap of the&amp;nbsp;NavVis&#39; cloud-based&amp;nbsp;3d visualization software&amp;nbsp;appeal to&amp;nbsp;you?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16777215,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:180,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;In this role, you will&amp;nbsp;closely work&amp;nbsp;with our engineers, UX designers, product managers, and customer-facing teams, to&amp;nbsp;determine&amp;nbsp;strategic priorities and translate them into product enhancements. You will be a crucial part of our Product Reality Access team, which manages&amp;nbsp;NavVis&amp;nbsp;IVION and NVC products.&amp;nbsp;People that are part of this team actively shape the future of 3D reality capture and visualization technologies, bringing&amp;nbsp;state-of-the-art&amp;nbsp;cloud-based software to customers around the globe.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16777215,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:180,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are looking for your&amp;nbsp;expertise&amp;nbsp;to shape&amp;nbsp;the discovery &amp;amp; development processes and further&amp;nbsp;empower&amp;nbsp;our product teams!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16777215,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:180,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;HOW YOU WILL MAKE AN IMPACT&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;2&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;You will use your curiosity for continuous improvement by&amp;nbsp;deep-diving&amp;nbsp;into our customers&#39; needs, their&amp;nbsp;&quot;job-to-be-done&quot; and&amp;nbsp;workflows, as well as the reality capture industry&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16777215,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;3355597

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://3339696.fs1.hubspotusercontent-na1.net/hubfs/3339696/greenhouse_hero.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;900&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;THE OPPORTUNITY&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for an Enterprise Project Manager to lead high-impact reality capture projects for our largest industrial clients across North America.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you’ll manage the full lifecycle of 3D reality capture projects, from initial scoping and stakeholder alignment to execution and delivery of high-fidelity digital twins. You’ll coordinate closely with clients, internal teams, and our network of global service providers to ensure projects are executed efficiently on budget, on time, and to the highest quality standards.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a unique opportunity to join an international, high-growth tech company, be part of the largest reality capture projects in the industry and directly influence how major enterprises digitize their Industrial assets.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;mark&quot; data-prosemirror-mark-name=&quot;strong&quot;&gt;This is a fixed term position running through December 2027&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;HOW YOU WILL MAKE AN IMPACT&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead end-to-end execution of large-scale reality capture, 3D laser scanning and surveying projects for enterprise clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the primary point of contact for customers, managing all communication, timelines, and expectations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define project scopes, deliverables, budgets, and success metrics with precision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate internal teams (Sales, Customer Success, Data Operations, Product) and external service providers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor, steer and report project progress to ensure timely and successful delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot challenges and develop scalable solutions in collaboration with cross-functional teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute directly to company revenue and customer satisfaction by delivering high-value outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Further optimize, streamline and automate internal Project Management standards and data delivery workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;WHAT WILL HELP YOU SUCCEED IN THE ROLE&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educational background in Civil Engineering, Technical Geography (GIS/Geomatics), Geodesy, Geo-informatics, Surveying, or similar.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on/field experience executing reality capture, laser scanning, or surveying work, preferably in highly complex industrial environments (e.g., automotive, oil &amp;amp; gas).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project management experience in reality capture, laser scanning, surveying, or similar technical domains.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with 3D laser scanning and surveying data (respective data processing and QC/QA) is a big plus.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to manage complex, multi-stakeholder projects with tight deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working with enterprise-level clients and international subcontractors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent organizational and communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Structured work style with an intrinsic motivation for optimizations and efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to travel up to 30% and comfortable in industrial environments that may require safety training, working from heights, narrow areas and random drug screenings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Language skills: English&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
