&lt;h3&gt;THE OPPORTUNITY&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Does&amp;nbsp;owning&amp;nbsp;and scaling an internal data and analytics platform that powers decision-making across the organization appeal to you?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;In this role, you will lead the evolution of our internal data and analytics platform — from both a technical and product perspective. You will work closely with Product, Engineering, and business stakeholders to define priorities, shape the platform roadmap, and ensure teams have reliable, trustworthy data to make informed decisions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
