&lt;h3&gt;THE OPPORTUNITY&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-local-id=&quot;142771756267&quot; data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot; data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot;&gt;In this role, you will join the NavVis Mobile Team and use your deep expertise in Android development to shape the future of NavVis IVION Go — our mobile app that lets users dive into rich digital data around them, wherever they go. You will leverage the powerful digital twins created with our mobile mapping devices NavVis VLX/MLX as well as our cutting-edge visual positioning technology to create spatially aware user experiences for our manufacturing clients around the world.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-local-id=&quot;65dea358e014&quot; data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;If you&#39;re passionate about clean code and elegant design, &lt;span id=&quot;f9a135d9-2a87-4cc9-8ebd-5afc13ac6519&quot; data-mark-type=&quot;annotation&quot; data-mark-annotation-type=&quot;inlineComment&quot; data-id=&quot;f9a135d9-2a87-4cc9-8ebd-5afc13ac6519&quot; data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;mark&quot; data-prosemirror-mark-name=&quot;annotation&quot;&gt;keeping up to date with&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span id=&quot;ad65db13-0355-4601-af86-08ede8631d27&quot; data-mark-type=&quot;annotation&quot; data-mark-annotation-type=&quot;inlineComment&quot; data-id=&quot;ad65db13-0355-4601-af86-08ede8631d27&quot; data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;mark&quot; data-prosemirror-mark-name=&quot;annotation&quot;&gt;current &lt;/span&gt;Android ecosystem, and love building with modern toolchains — you might be exactly who we&#39;re looking for!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
